# LLM Platform

## Setup

### Kubernetes Secrets

To deploy services that require a Hugging Face token, you'll need to create a Kubernetes secret in the cluster.

Run the following command, replacing `'your-hugging-face-token'` with your actual token:

```bash
kubectl create secret generic huggingface-secret --from-literal=hf_token='your-hugging-face-token'
```
